urlLink What's Worming Our Way  If you want to even think about what the enemy might have in store for your computer this article is pretty interesting.  It's not comforting.  If you are interested in science fiction and information technology it doesn't take too much imagination to see a scenario down the road a bit where information wars are waged against corporations and governments and the defenders try to stay one step ahead.  Oops. . . or, is that where we are now?  --Buck